<div id="about-the-community" class="section-spacer">
    <h2 class="sect-title">About Seton</h2>
    <div class="col-grid-2">
        <div>
            <p class="par-lg">Here are some reasons to live in Seton: </p>
            <h3>Community Interaction and Engagement</h3>
            <p class="par-lg">Seton has created an environment where people can meet and connect with the community by establishing parks for spending leisure time and pathways for taking walks. You can easily find people to connect with while doing what you love.</p>

            <h3>AgeCare in Seton</h3>
            <p class="par-lg">If you are a senior, you aren't left out as there's a fantastic community for seniors known as AgeCare. The Seniors Community has been attending to the needs of Seniors in other parts of Calgary, such as Alberta. The good news is that they are now in Seton. AgeCare is situated close to the South Health Campus and aims to give seniors a sense of community life. They provide a 24 hr service for seniors, amenities, and avenues for recreation. AgeCare residents can live a quality life even as they get older in Seton.</p>
        </div>
